videos.headline: Moss' second TD extends Utah's lead
videos.description: Zack Moss lowers his shoulder and trucks the defender to score a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Williams scores Utah's 3rd rushing TD
videos.description: Troy Williams snaps the ball and fakes the defense with a delayed draw to score a 8-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Utah continues to dominate  with 4th rushing TD
videos.description: Troy Williams runs a zone read and takes it in for a 9-yard touchdown to give Utah a 28-0 lead.

videos.headline: Lindsay's rushing TD puts Colorado on the board
videos.description: Phillip Lindsay runs through a gauntlet of defenders for a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Colorado showing some fight with Montez rushing TD
videos.description: Steven Montez fakes the pitch and runs to the left side for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Utah recovers fumble on strip sack
videos.description: Bradlee Anae sacks Steven Montez and Cody Barton picks up the fumble and returns it 13 yards.
